(155, 'widget_integral_testimonial', 'a:4:{i:1;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:44:"Priscilla Nunn, CEO - Your Training Partners";s:8:"textarea";s:180:"I spent over 2 hours trying to customize another theme and had to scrap it. I spent less than 30 minutes on this theme and it was fun.  And the customer service has been fantastic!";s:9:"image_url";s:74:"http://demo.themely.com/integral/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/about-pic2.jpg";}i:2;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:40:"Malcolm Reynolds, Captain - The Serenity";s:8:"textarea";s:201:"Come a day there won''t be room for naughty men like us to slip about at all. This job goes south, there well may not be another. So here is us, on the raggedy edge. Don''t push me, and I won''t push you.";s:9:"image_url";s:74:"http://demo.themely.com/integral/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/about-pic3.jpg";}i:3;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:32:"River Tam, Sister - The Serenity";s:8:"textarea";s:179:"People don''t like to be meddled with. We tell that to do, what to think. Don''t run, don''t walk. We''re in their homes and in their heads and we haven''t the right. We''re meddlesome.";s:9:"image_url";s:73:"http://demo.themely.com/integral/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/about-pic.jpg";}s:12:"_multiwidget";i:1;}', 'yes'),
